#: ../../source/acquisitions.rst:853
msgid ""
"From here you can find a file to upload and/or see the files you have "
"already attached."
msgstr ""
"Da qui è possibile trovare un file da caricare e / o vedere i file già "
"allegati."

#: ../../source/acquisitions.rst:856
msgid "|image855|"
msgstr "|image855|"

